{"tid":1903983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位[s]高登[/s]連登手足！今天！熱血公民！正式！成立八周年啦！","createTime":"2020-02-29T10:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T10:47:57.000Z","uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85c9e161bbc73f3c827e7bd37720adce9be58425","tid":1903983,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/29/sAE7Qx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F29%2FsAE7Qx.jpg&h=aa4350da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天，是 #熱血公民 成立八周年。<br />\n<br />\n其實哪一天才算做正式成立呢？不同組織有不同計算方法，當年，熱血公民並沒有選擇在某一天正式公開宣布成立，所以也不會有所謂「正式誕生」的日子。<br />\n那麼，為什麼是2月29日呢？是否胡亂選一天？當然不是，因為八年前今日，有一件事發生了，這件事決定了熱血公民的存亡，令這個黨可以真正誕生，所以我才選這一天作為誕日。<br />\n至於當日發生了什麼事？如果這個黨能挨到十二周年，我才考慮公開吧。<br />\n<br />\n黨慶剛好是2月29日，四年才有一次，也讓我覺得正好，不用年年搞慶典，也讓大家更珍惜整個黨，想要再搞慶生會，起埋要令個黨挨多四年啊！<br />\n<br />\n八年過去，由一開始只有十幾個人的小組，發展到今日的規模，實在不容易。<br />\n感謝八年來，所有曾經支持過熱血公民的朋友，多年來，熱血公民得到很多朋友的關照、愛護、幫助，無言感激。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望提醒一眾熱狗，熱血公民創立的原點，是源於兩個字：夢想！<br />\n這是一個為了實現夢想而成立的組織。<br />\n<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達<br />\n29/02/2020"},{"pid":"4cf5e6c279d4cf3460ffa0891e5e5d22e82c29f7","tid":1903983,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F200846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=62af040e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce7HFHp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe7HFHp.gif&h=44eceebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/224406_831446b041983396bf0ecbff2a6d554c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F224406_831446b041983396bf0ecbff2a6d554c.gif&h=1de75683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTXn3cqVOpnZmVgZEyFFzBBSXfQnEadHaG1xtjHjz7mySqa3W0q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTXn3cqVOpnZmVgZEyFFzBBSXfQnEadHaG1xtjHjz7mySqa3W0q&h=ff43082f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60659a107a35f252bd4340a00c02d8f85d4c7c6c","tid":1903983,"uid":299164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"「行動 post」毋忘831<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1903302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1903302</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/87770024_2231758317118531_6310337603946151936_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=5kqlrwTk0ioAX-O4f7e&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=1ed77cfb7fc8f2db04ca60b001ae1d28&amp;oe=5EB57D1D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F87770024_2231758317118531_6310337603946151936_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3D5kqlrwTk0ioAX-O4f7e%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D14%26oh%3D1ed77cfb7fc8f2db04ca60b001ae1d28%26oe%3D5EB57D1D&h=363a4fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c5df104655f0bb2ee99b0ce83b2bcf24204adbb","tid":1903983,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"}]}